@host = http://localhost:7071

### Scenario 1: Inventory availability
POST {{host}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Do we have ITEM-123 in warehouse MAD? What's available and ETA?"
}

### Scenario 2: Draft sales order
POST {{host}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Create a draft order for ACME: 10x ITEM-123, ship tomorrow."
}

### Scenario 3: Order exception copilot
POST {{host}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Why is SO-456 delayed and what should I do?"
}
